## 13. Human-in-the-Loop — When the AI Asks for Help

**File:** `backend/src/lib/agentic/humanLoop.ts` (111 lines)

Mike has a sophisticated human-in-the-loop system that pauses execution when the AI needs human input.

### 13.1 Types of Human Loop Events

| Type | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| **Approval Required** | Plan approval before execution |
| **Clarifying Question** | Free text, single choice, multi choice, or confirmation |
| **File Request** | Need a document from the user |
| **Blocking Question** | Must be answered before execution continues |

### 13.2 Approval Flow

```
AI generates plan
    │
    ▼
